<br>
16-24 go pretty fast because there are some great xp spots (unrest, paludal, etc.).  I recommend that you buy lvl 16 and lvl 20 pets at one time to save the return trip or stick with the store bought.  Expensive, but leaving a good group during a sweet xp run sucks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=outofmana>OutOfMana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#333333>(1/23/03 9:57:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1786.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Directions</span><hr size=1> If you are as good at misreading things as I am, Barmo's directions will get you lost (I read it as having all the islands to the left of the boat).<br>
<br>
